data.description: Are you wanting to see the best sunsets on Lake Buchanan!  There are numerous spots to sit and enjoy them every night you will never get tired of them.  The house is a 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom and is approximately 1975 sq. ft.  It sits on 4 1/2 lots and is .63 of an acre.  There is a detached garage that has 2 doors to make it easy to be used as a workshop or a place to store your boat or jet skis and also a 1 car garage attached to the house.  All the roofs have been replaced recenlty.  There is tons of storage in the Master bedroom with a walk in closet and built in storage cabnits.  If you need a place to do your crafts or garden there is a place for you to do that.  You're  just minutes away from Spider Mountain Bike park, and all the other great things the Hill Country has to offer.
